    - [inld_qualname, IncrementalNewlineDecoder.__qualname__.__eq__, ["IncrementalNewlineDecoder"], true, "io.IncrementalNewlineDecoder.__qualname__ == 'IncrementalNewlineDecoder' — simple unqualified class name; confirmed Python 3.14.3 macOS"]

